<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Vigilance & Compliance</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/aos/2.3.4/aos.css">
    
    <style>
        /* Vigilance Section Styling */
        .vigilance-section {
            padding: 50px 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        /* Section Headers */
        h2, h3 {
            color: #d9534f;
        }

        /* Form Styling */
        .form-control, .form-select {
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        textarea.form-control {
            height: 120px;
            resize: none;
        }

        /* Submit Button */
        .btn-danger {
            width: 100%;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .btn-danger:hover {
            background-color: #c9302c;
        }

        /* FAQ Section */
        p strong {
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Card Effects */
        .card {
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container vigilance-section">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Vigilance & Compliance</h2>
        
        <h3>Vigilance Guidelines</h3>
        <p>Our vigilance department ensures transparency and integrity...</p>
        <p>Contact: vigilance@shipyard.com | +123 456 7890</p>
        
        <h3 class="mt-5">Report an Issue</h3>
        <form action="/vigilance/report" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">Name (Optional)</label>
                <input type="text" name="name" class="form-control">
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">Contact Details (Optional)</label>
                <input type="text" name="contactDetails" class="form-control">
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">Type of Complaint</label>
                <select name="complaintType" class="form-select" required>
                    <option value="Fraud">Fraud</option>
                    <option value="Corruption">Corruption</option>
                    <option value="Safety Violation">Safety Violation</option>
                    <option value="Harassment">Harassment</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">Detailed Description</label>
                <textarea name="description" class="form-control" required></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">Attach Evidence (Optional)</label>
                <input type="file" name="evidence" class="form-control">
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">Submit Report</button>
        </form>
        
        <h3 class="mt-5">FAQs on Vigilance</h3>
        <p><strong>Q: How is my report handled?</strong></p>
        <p>A: Your report is reviewed by the vigilance team confidentially...</p>
        <p><strong>Q: Will my identity remain confidential?</strong></p>
        <p>A: Yes, reports can be submitted anonymously.</p>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/aos/2.3.4/aos.js"></script>
    <script>
        AOS.init();
    </script>

</body>
</html>
